The paper deals with characterising preorders on labelled transition systems that respect safety and liveness properties, which are topics commonly studied in the areas of logic and verification (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), formal methods (cs.FL), and temporal logic (cs.LT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
